<!--
	Kitsune Vehicle Overhaul — items.xml

	Two-pronged approach:
	1. VehicleSelfDamage reduction per vehicle class (stacks with Grease Monkey)
	2. Modest HP buffs as a secondary buffer

	Self-damage formula: raw × EffectSelfDamagePer
	Grease Monkey already gives -20% per rank. Our values stack additively.

	Supports: Vanilla + Bdub's Vehicles
-->
